Ask HN: Near future climate change scenarios?
text:
I'm looking for possible realistic near future scenarios regarding climate change to communicate better with people who think everything's going to be fine.

The more precise, the better. Both worst-case scenarios (people start wars over water) and best-case scenarios (politics is turned upside down and focuses primarily on how avoid more catastrophies) are welcome.

Ask HN: Tips on sketching diagrams/mind-maps?
text:
I often sketch diagrams when trying to understand something, such as a software system or mathematical proof, but my diagrams always end up messy and inconsistent. Formal diagram systems (e.g. UML or ERD) are generally too complex or domain-specific for quickly mapping things out on paper.

Do you have a general approach to sketching out a concept or system? Even if not, miscellaneous tips and rules-of-thumb are welcome.
